{"tid":729501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【暗殺抗暴政？】菲律賓不足48小時內　 再有地方首長被槍擊暗殺","createTime":"2018-07-04T15:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:56:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2018961bd8137a90f7ead6386d240f9221bcab85","tid":729501,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1405045_1_L_20180704060030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1405045_1_L_20180704060030.jpg&h=82cdf493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓不足48小時內，兩名地方首長遭槍殺。<br />\n<br />\n最新一宗兇案在呂宋中部地區發生，提尼奧將軍鎮鎮長博特，昨天下午在甲萬那端市，被騎電單車的槍手開槍打死。<br />\n<br />\n報道指博特坐的車滿佈子彈孔，穿黑衣的槍手逃去。<br />\n<br />\n另外在前日上午，首都馬尼拉以南60多公里的塔納萬市，市長哈利利在市政府廣場前參加升旗典禮時，遭人從遠處開槍射殺。"},{"pid":"a7144dd8dda18779e2f4be407ccf2f92097b6b2d","tid":729501,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"未經審訊亂屈人殺人, 始終要還"},{"pid":"ed44244e568a3b3585dd99e817ba297b4a5810fe","tid":729501,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:22:54.000Z","msg":"菲律賓想洗底就黎香港"},{"pid":"b6d9a1b5bce53dd4f4fa3737366074195a38d371","tid":729501,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59d24ceb2f92e276f74c24e2f254a7ae7051fc17","tid":729501,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"杜特爾特去咗邊？唔係串柒柒架咩？出黎啦，唔係龜縮下話？"},{"pid":"ca56a9699d436b3d376e07c5695f00f8482e0405","tid":729501,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d9a1b5bce53dd4f4fa3737366074195a38d371","tid":729501,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fac